WORKDIR(2)               System Calls Manual              WORKDIR(2)

NAME
       workdir - get the current working directory

SYNOPSIS
       include "workdir.m";
       workdir := load Workdir Workdir->PATH;

       init:  fn(): string;

DESCRIPTION
       Workdir returns a string representation of the working direc‚Äê
       tory of the invoking process.

       When Inferno boots, the initial process has / for its working
       directory.

SOURCE
       /appl/lib/workdir.b

SEE ALSO
       sys-chdir(2), sys-fd2path(2), sys-stat(2)

